\newlabel{fig:economics}{{6}{8}{Production cost reduction (6 agents, 788 spawns/day). (a) Cumulative token consumption over 30 days: 88\% boot savings. (b) Monthly cost: \$2,061/mo saved on Sonnet, \$10,305/mo on Opus. (c) Per-agent breakdown: boot waste (red) vs. productive work (blue)}{figure.caption.13}{}}
